#| msgid ""
#| "`SQLite <https://sqlite.org/>`_ is a relational database management "
#| "system, written in C programming library. SQLite is not directly "
#| "comparable to client/server SQL database engines such as MySQL, Oracle or "
#| "PostgreSQL. Rather, it is an embedded SQL database engine, i.e. it is "
#| "embedded in an end program. SQLite reads and writes directly to ordinary "
#| "disk files. For device-local storage with low writer concurrency and less "
#| "than a terabyte of content, SQLite is almost always a better solution. "
#| "SQLite is fast and reliable and it requires no configuration or "
#| "maintenance. It keeps things simple. SQLite \"just works\"."
msgid ""
"`SQLite <https://sqlite.org/>`_ is a relational database management system, "
"written in the C programming library. SQLite is not directly comparable to "
"client/server SQL database engines such as MySQL, Oracle or PostgreSQL. "
"Rather, it is an SQL database engine that is embedded in an end program. "
"SQLite reads and writes directly to ordinary disk files. SQLite is almost "
"always the best solution for device-local storage with low write-concurrency "
"and less than a terabyte of content. SQLite is fast and reliable and it "
"requires no configuration or maintenance. It keeps things simple. SQLite "
"\"just works\"."
msgstr ""
"El `SQLite <https://sqlite.org/>`_ és un sistema per a la gestió d'una base "
"de dades relacional, escrita en la biblioteca de programació C. El SQLite no "
"és directament comparable amb els motors de bases de dades SQL client/"
"servidor, com ara el MySQL, Oracle o PostgreSQL. Més aviat, és un motor de "
"base de dades SQL incrustat, és a dir, que està incrustat en un programa "
"final. El SQLite llegeix i escriu directament a fitxers de disc normals. Per "
"a l'emmagatzematge en el dispositiu local amb una concurrència baixa en "
"l'escriptura i menys d'un terabyte de contingut, el SQLite és gairebé sempre "
"una solució millor. És ràpid i fiable, i no requereix cap configuració o "
"manteniment. Manté les coses senzilles. El SQLite «senzillament funciona»."

